    </p>

    <h2 class="section-title">Our North Star</h2>

    <p>
      To build on this, we created a North Star for the Funding Service. It gives us a clear way to assess value, make trade offs, and focus on service wide outcomes.
    </p>

    <ul class="list">
      <li>sustain operational excellence</li>
      <li>build service agility, efficiency, and resilience</li>
      <li>increase certainty for providers</li>
      <li>grow the number of grants delivered</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      The North Star focuses on capabilities rather than systems...
